What will game do

    Game Menu
        Pre Game Setup
        *Two grids showing player and enemy boards
            -Grid class with collected cells and attibutes
            -Grid buttons should be stylised correctly, with sharp corners
            -Ship art should be created for hit, and intact
        *There will be a ready button after placing ships
        * 4 Ships with sized 5-4-3-3-2
        *they will be showing on below player board
        *With drag&drop player will place the ships and when hit "ready" button game will start
        *When hit ready, the wsame szied ships will be placed randomly on enemy board

        In game Setup
        *Player will start by shooting one grid on enemy ship and if hit, the turn will continue
        *When missed the turn will be sent to enemy and after thinking for 3 seconds, enemy will hit a random unhit cell
            -Enemy should collect cells that are hit, for avoiding hit to the same cell
        *When enemy hits, enemy will try to hit an adjacent cell
        *When enemy misses the turn will be sent to player and game will continue untill one of the players will lose all ships.


